node.accessibility_caption: Photo by beyond! on April 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, rose and outdoors.

node.text:
GOODBYE TEENAGE YEARS 🖤
im not gon lie, being 20 doesn’t feel real to me. im not to fond of the idea that I’ll never be a teenager again, but im ready for what life has in store for me.. thank you for being part of this journey, watching me grow up to be the person I am today. If you’re reading this, you are family to me, I will forever be here for anyone who needs me. love y’all til the end of me ☠️🖤🖤 gang! IM 20. Alr late 🤓
